import daicuong from './Đại cương.json'
import giaibieu from './Giải biểu.json'
import taha from './Tả hạ.json'
import phuongthuocsonggiaibieuly from './Phương-thuốc-song-giải-biểu-lý.json'
import thanhnhiet from './Thanh-nhiệt.json'
import truphong from './Trừ-phong.json'

export const questions = []
  .concat(
    daicuong,
    giaibieu,
    taha,
    phuongthuocsonggiaibieuly,
    thanhnhiet,
    truphong
  )
  .forEach((question) => question.answerOptions.sort(() => Math.random() - 0.5))
